r das Potential und Auswirkungen von Blockchains auf das eigene Unternehmen zu erkennen. Abschließend werden die Aspekte des Vertrauens und der Sicherheit erörtert. Das Buch bildet die Grundlage eines dreitägigen Seminars an der Fachhochschule Nordwestschweiz und eignet sich auch zum Selbststudium.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 04. Okt 2022) 0aBanks and bankingxTechnological innovations. 0aBitcoin. 0aElectronic commerce. 0aElectronic funds transfers. 0aFinancial institutionsxTechnological innovations. 0aMobile commerce. 4aBusiness-Management. 4aData-Management. 4aIT-Management. 4aIT-Security. 4aProzess-Management. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Information Management.2bisacsh  aIT management.  aIT security.  abusiness management.  adata management.  aprocess management.1 aBurgwinkel, Daniel, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBurgwinkel, Daniel, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aKienzler, Romeo, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMerz, Michael, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPloom, Martin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPloom, Tarmo, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aTosovic, Vladimir, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWildhaber, Bruno, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2016 Part 1z978311076250108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2016z978311070100508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2016z9783110485103oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE 